(firstQuint)Study for the Recording of Adherence to Treatment With Perindopril/Indapamide/Amlodipine Fixed Dose Combination.

 This is a non-interventional study aiming to record adherence to treatment with Perindopril/Indapamide/Amlodipine fixed dose combination.

 In parallel blood pressure levels will be recorded, as well as safety and tolerability of this fixed dose combination.

